################
# Nethack python interface assumes certain config options 
# and Nethack is NAO Version 3.4.3
#
# Vital options:
# OPTIONS=vt_tiledata
# OPTIONS=number_pad:1
#
# Planned option:
# OPTIONS=mouse_support
#
# Note: Options that only affect colors don't make a difference
################

